sentences: Noah Jacob Urrea (born March 31, 2001) is an American singer, actor, composer, dancer and model.
He represents the United States in the international pop group Now United.

section: == Career == | === 2011–2015: Early acting career ===

sentences: He had his first chance as an artist in 2011, when he appeared in Blake Shelton's music video, "Honey Bee".
section: == Career == | === 2011–2015: Early acting career ===

sentences: In 2012, Urrea was selected as one of Nickelodeon's 'Groundlings', where he developed the talent for improvised comedy.

sentences: Urrea made his film debut in 2013 with a role in A Madea Christmas, in which he acted and sang.
